+ Ingest from\nMessage Buses
++ Supported Sources
+++_ Apache Kafka
+++_ Azure Event Hubs (Kafka-compatible)
+++_ Amazon Kinesis, Google Pub/Sub
++ SQL Syntax
+++_ STREAM read_kafka(bootstrapServers, subscribe)
+++_ CREATE OR REFRESH STREAMING TABLE
-- Python Syntax
---_ spark.readStream.format("kafka")
---_ KAFKA_OPTIONS dict with auth config
---_ @dp.table decorator
-- Security
---_ Store connection string in Databricks Secrets
---_ Use pipeline parameters for non-sensitive config
---_ SASL_SSL + PLAIN mechanism for Event Hubs
-- Schema Handling
---_ Binary key/value → cast to string
---_ Parse JSON payload with from_json()
@endmindmap
